text: The outgoing Obama team gave the Trump team a pandemic playbook. If they’d followed it, the guidance questions would have led them, for instance, to stockpile masks & gowns, critical equipment now in short supply. But they ignored that guidance.  https://t.co/YRYGbMQnaP
